cache/
.claude/plans/
*.pyc
__pycache__/

# Eval: stray files written by arm agents during a grid run (not harness inputs).
# Robust approach: ignore ALL loose .md directly in a task dir, then un-ignore the
# exactly-4 known harness files. Arm deliverables (scope.md, plan.md, whatever they
# name it) are caught generically; harness inputs are explicitly kept.
eval/**/.claude/
eval/tasks/*/results/
eval/tasks/*/*.md
!eval/tasks/*/task.md
!eval/tasks/*/tells.md
!eval/tasks/*/skills.md
!eval/tasks/*/rubric.md
